/* Ques 9:-
(Area and perimeter of a rectangle) Write a program that displays the area and
perimeter of a rectangle with the width of 4.5 and height of 7.9 using the following
formula:
area = width * height
*/

public class Nine 
{
    public static void main(String[] args) 
    {
        System.out.println("area of rectangle is :- " + 4.5 * 7.9); 
        System.out.println("Perimeter of rectangle is :- " + (7.9 + 4.5 + 7.9 + 4.5));
        
    }
}



/* Output:-

area of rectangle is :- 35.550000000000004
Perimeter of rectangle is :- 24.8

*/
